##  Fractional degrees format, e.g. 30.55 degrees </description> </item><item><term> 
## DegreesMinutes</term><description> 
##  Degrees minutes format, e.g. 30 degrees 30" </description> </item><item><term> 
## DegreesMinutesSeconds</term><description> 
##  Degrees minutes seconds format, e.g. 30 degrees 30"30' </description> </item><item><term> 
## WholeDegrees</term><description> 
##  Whole degrees only, e.g. 30 degrees </description> </item></list>
